{"tid":2157722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★勞工處下周舉辦網上招聘會 提供逾1200個職 月薪介乎1萬至2.1萬港元","createTime":"2020-08-15T08:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T07:02:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"97f1246d4264f75f758d846a88ec5cf2d7400280","tid":2157722,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"勞工處今日宣布，下周二(18日)及周三(19日)下午6時，會在互動就業服務網站（<a href=\"http://www.jobs.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jobs.gov.hk&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8ajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=190eb9d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.jobs.gov.hk</a>）舉辦「開創新天地網上招聘會」，是次招聘會共提供1200個職位，月薪介乎1萬至2.1萬港元之間。<br />\n<br />\n勞工處表示，招聘會有34間機構參與，主要來自物業管理、商用服務及飲食業，涵蓋化學實習生、康體助理、客戶服務主任、會計文員、診所助理、行政助理、麵包師、技術員及工程師等職位，合共提供逾1200個職位空缺。求職者只需預先登記成為勞工處互動就業服務的用戶，即可於招聘會舉行期間向參加機構網上遞交求職申請，費用全免。<br />\n<br />\n招聘會約83%職位是全職空缺，大部分月薪介乎1萬至2.1萬港元；約92%的職位空缺學歷要求為中六或以下；約79%的職位空缺無需相關工作經驗，適合應屆畢業生申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200815/bkn-20200815100720476-0815_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200815%2Fbkn-20200815100720476-0815_00822_001.html&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8ajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=f936f1be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200815/bkn-20200815100720476-0815_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3c5f3725d23984186189f668d6ffe7ec38122f57","tid":2157722,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:23:41.000Z","msg":"大部分月薪介乎<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>1萬</strong></span>至2.1萬港元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cfc46503158b8db45ceeed1a1efa35daf3fd64",